name: - On the way to the village of Sherpa Gaon (Nepal series #33) -
description:
On our way back to the village of Syabrubesi, the starting point of the Langtang trek. We took a slightly different route because Jay (my guide) wanted to take me to a Sherpa wedding in Sherpa Gaon (Rasuwa Nepal).
